  "anime_id" : 19939,
  "description" : "Ten thousand races roared, tearing the heavens asunder! The Age of Class Awakening had fully arrived! On the Day of Awakening, Li Yi awakened to the supreme Yin Spirit class — Supreme of the Underworld! As the Book of Life and Death turned its pages, the lifespan of all souls was his to decide; as the Wheel of Reincarnation spun, the departed spirits of every realm fell under his command! One hundred thousand ghost generals, one million shadow soldiers — a single thought to sever life, a single thought to sever death. Across all heavens and realms, he stood supreme — his will was the will of Heaven itself! In the face of fiend slaughter, as the human race`s lament echoed across the universe, Li Yi shattered the shackles of his class and ascended to become The Great Emperor of Fengdu, standing toe-to-toe against the three great evil gods of the fiend races! As the master of the Underworld, he held dominion over life and death — and stood as the guardian of all living beings! That battle shook the heavens and the earth! In the end, Li Yi destroyed the evil gods and their fiend race, bringing peace and tranquility back to this battered world once more!\nsource: youku.tv",
